 <H1>Views</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>A view is just a relation, but we store a definition, rather than a set of tuples.</H2>
</UL></P>
<P><UL>
CREATE  VIEW  ActiveSailors (name, age, day)
<BR></UL><UL>
	AS  SELECT   S.sname, S.age, R.day 
</UL><UL>
	FROM  Sailors S, Reserves R
</UL><UL>
	WHERE  S.name=R.sname  AND  S.rating&#0626</UL></P>
<P><UL>
<LI>Views can be dropped using the DROP VIEW command.
